Usage:

python main.py filename

When the program is running, you can press
	- A		to switch to adaptive threshold
	- C		to switch to color threshold
	- T		to toggle between tracking on/off 

-----------------------------------------------------------------
The color we used for different videos are:
(In order of BGR)

Bottle:			(30,130,130)
Book:			(30,10,180)
Bag:			(100,255,200)

To change colors, search in main for COLOR and replace the tuple
------------------------------------------------------------------
The parameters we used for adaptive threshold on the images are:

Book: 			(5,5) opening + (6,6) opening on the mask
Bottle:			(3,3) opening + (4,4) opening on the mask
Bag:			did not find any parameter that works well

------------------------------------------------------------------
